---
title: Grilled Montreal-Spiced Double Striploin Steak and Chipotle Shrimp Cocktail  with Grilled Asparagus and Potatoes
description: Give the father figure in your life the best gift—time to grill! Flame-kissed, Montreal-spiced steaks, jumbo shrimp, asparagus and roasted potatoes are on the menu, with a side of DIY cocktail sauce.
